# Release Gate Rules for AICostPlanner

## Pre-Release Checklist

### Build Verification
- [ ] `npm run build` succeeds
- [ ] No TypeScript errors
- [ ] No Astro errors
- [ ] All pages generate

### Validator Results
- [ ] `npm run validate:content` passes
- [ ] `npm run validate:claims` passes (0 banned claims)
- [ ] `npm run validate:links` passes
- [ ] `npm run validate:sitemap-llms` passes
- [ ] `npm run validate:jsonld` passes

### Content Verification
- [ ] All titles unique
- [ ] All meta descriptions unique
- [ ] All H1s unique
- [ ] All canonicals present and absolute
- [ ] All JSON-LD URLs absolute
- [ ] AI Summary on every page
- [ ] FAQ on every page
- [ ] Last updated date on every page

### CTA Verification
- [ ] Primary CTA URL correct: `https://app.rutaapi.com/register?lng=en`
- [ ] Secondary CTA URL correct: `https://app.rutaapi.com/pricing`
- [ ] No other external CTAs

### Contamination Check
- [ ] No LinkAI references
- [ ] No AI API Doctor references
- [ ] No aiapiprice.com references
- [ ] No AI API Radar references
- [ ] No SellerFixHub references
- [ ] No ExtensionFixes references

