## Production Deployment

### Pre-Deploy
1. All local checks pass
2. Validators pass
3. Git commit with message

### Post-Deploy
1. Homepage returns 200
2. All full pages return 200
3. sitemap.xml returns 200
4. robots.txt returns 200
5. llms.txt returns 200

### Cache-Busted Check
1. Homepage title correct
2. Homepage H1 correct
3. Homepage canonical correct
4. CTA hrefs correct

## Final Gates

### FOUNDATION_READY
- Local build + validators pass
- Production verification pending

### PRODUCTION_READY
- Local build + validators pass
- Production live checks pass

## Never Claim

"Doing" or "Done" until:
1. Build passes
2. All validators pass
3. Production verified (if applicable)

## Commands

```bash
# Full verification
npm run verify

# Individual
npm run validate:content
npm run validate:claims
npm run validate:links
npm run validate:sitemap-llms
npm run validate:jsonld

# Build
npm run build

# Preview
npm run preview
```
